commit.message: Remove unused .git_hooks (the upstream repo is archived)
Bump 3.0.3

Fix rst README and use it for long description

`tox` failed because `README.md` was not found.
Bump 3.0.2
Add long description
Fix warnings when generating documentation
Ignore Makefile.custom.config

Remove conditional dependency on old version of cairosvg

It was required for Python 2 which is no more supported.
Update changelog
Add minimal `shell.nix` for development
Drop python<=3.7 support

Use `importlib_metadata` instead of `importlib.metadata`

Make it backward compatible with every supported Python version.
Could be a fix to #545.

Drop unmaintained `pytest-flake8`

Just call `flake8` instead.

See
- https://github.com/tholo/pytest-flake8/issues/98
- https://github.com/tholo/pytest-flake8/issues/92
